➜千吨燃油毁了曾经的天堂：毛里求斯海域漏油影响“极其可怕”
http://www.sohu.com/a/412959774_260616	32631
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
